# Reflex-plattform a special Haskell-Nix project

The project try-reflex installs a nix shell. Here are some commands:

### List version of a Haskell package:

    nix-env -f '<nixpkgs>' -qaPA haskellPackages|grep myPackage

Use package name instead of myPackage